00:29:58.740 --> 00:30:02.410
So one of the themes we'll talk
about a lot in the course

00:30:02.410 --> 00:30:05.280
is both an amazing power of the
human mind and an amazing

00:30:05.280 --> 00:30:06.770
peril of the human mind.

00:30:06.770 --> 00:30:09.250
And it's what psychologists
call automaticity.

00:30:09.250 --> 00:30:12.430
It's that our mind, in order
to be efficient and quick,

00:30:12.430 --> 00:30:14.940
