00:30:24.180 --> 00:30:27.700
It lets us do a lot of things.

00:30:27.700 --> 00:30:28.690
So that's the power of it.

00:30:28.690 --> 00:30:31.940
The peril is when something
becomes automatic, we lose

00:30:31.940 --> 00:30:35.460
control of it within
ourselves.

