00:35:44.070 --> 00:35:47.650
Why do you think people tend
to answer 10%, some 30%?

00:35:47.650 --> 00:35:50.490
Very few people give you
the mathematically

00:35:50.490 --> 00:35:51.430
correct answer of 70%.

00:35:51.430 --> 00:35:52.680
Why do they do that?

00:35:56.020 --> 00:36:00.100
Because they tend to think, how
often have I met somebody

00:36:00.100 --> 00:36:02.660
who has my exact birthday?

00:36:02.660 --> 00:36:03.820
And you go, not that often.

00:36:03.820 --> 00:36:06.320
It's not like every 30 people
I meet, somebody says, you

00:36:06.320 --> 00:36:07.590
